Thanks for your response. I tried on version r0.11 and r0.12 . Both raised this error. I suspect checkpoint. Similarly, this error was also raised when i tried to pre-train with inception-v3, vgg-19 model. I see the instruction on model slim page about this error, but i don't know the reason why the differential between the value of lhs shape in my error and in the instruction.
